    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "BAe 146\nAIRCAL\nSafety\nSecurite\nSeguridad\nSicherheit",
      "EVACUATION ROUTES\nOnce safely off, move quickly away\nfrom the aircraft.\nPULL\nEXIT DOORS - Rotate handle in\ndirection of arrow. Push door\noutward. If evacuation slide fails\nto inflate automatically, pull red\nloop to inflate. Remain standing,\nand then jump into slide.\nEXITS\nJUMP",
      "NO OPERATIONS DURING FLIGHT\nRADIOS\nDESK TOP\nCALCULATORS\nBUTANE\nLIGHTERS\n3 SEC.\n5 SEC.\n8 SEC.\n12. SEC."
    ],
